Homepage Statistics
 Overview
       Total Trucks on Service (This Year):
              Displays the count of trucks currently in service from the beginning of the current year. 
              This information is retrieved from the database and cached for optimal performance, updating daily.
       Total Orders Made:
              Shows the cumulative count of orders made since the inception of the system. 
              This data is sourced from the database and cached for efficient access, refreshed daily.
       Total Covered Kilometers:
              Presents the total distance covered by all trucks since the system's initiation. 
              This data is fetched from the database and cached, with updates occurring on a daily basis for real-time accuracy.

